{
  "text": "is the degree to which w is accepted by M . The above definitions provide a model of computing with values on fuzzy automata. We shall refer to the fuzzy automaton in Definition 1 as a fuzzy automaton for computing with values (or FACV for short). Within the framework of fuzzy automata, Ying [CITATION_1] proposed the following formal model of computing with words by extending further the fuzzy transition function of an FACV.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "20834671"
